extends /layouts/default

block content
    section.banner
        .container.content-bottom
            .content-box
                h1 Commercial Vinyl Flooring Project.<br/> Direct Provision Centre, Dublin.
        .bg
            img.image(src="/images/projects/banner-3.png", alt="image")

    section.case-study.bg-dark
        .container
            .case-panel
                figure.case-figure
                    img.image(src="/images/projects/image-2.png", alt="image")
                .content-box
                    +tag('CASE STUDY', 'white')
                    h3
                        img.icon(src="/icons/doc.svg", alt="image")
                        | Project Overview
                    p This commercial flooring project covered the full Direct Provision Centre in Clondalkin. Utilizing aesthetic appeal, as well as safety, our IVC Isafe70 commercial vinyl flooring conforms to the highest standard of European Safety Norms. Isafe 70 enhanced particles limit the risk of falling in various settings. An edgy and modern flooring adding spark to any space. The range includes various vivid colour combinations, traditional and modern woods and stunning concrete designs. Take a look at the photos to see how various colour and texture finishes work together.
                    p Underneath the IVC Flooring, we used a Damtec Acoustic Underlay 3mm to soundproof the floor effectively. This underlay can be used under parquet, laminate, or carpeting as well as under linoleum and PVC flooring.
                    .box
                        h5 Impact sound improvement (ISO 140‐8/ISO 717‐2):
                        ul
                            li ΔLw = 29dB with carpet
                            li ΔLw = 20dB under 8 mm laminate flooring
                            li ΔLw = 19dB under 13 mm parquetry
                            li ΔLw = 18dB under 16 mm solid parquetry
                            li ΔLw = 18dB under 9mm tiles
                    p An internal play area was also a big challenge for this project. For this, Virgo proved to be the ideal flooring as its light touch makes it feel like real grass, imitating a garden play area.

            .case-details
                .case-detail-box
                    h4
                        img.icon(src="/icons/feature.svg", alt="image")
                        | Featured Products
                    p
                        strong
                            a(href="/") Damtec 3mm Acoustic Underlay:
                        |  Premium insulating padding & sound dampening for concrete or wooden subfloor.
                    p
                        strong
                            a(href="/") Virgo 38mm Grass:
                        |  An extremely durable & low maintenance solution to traditional lawn grass.
                    p
                        strong
                            a(href="/") IVC Isafe 70 Colours:
                        |  An edgy vinyl flooring perfect for bringing any space to life.
                    p
                        strong
                            a(href="/") IVC Isafe 70 Woods :
                        |  An impeccable natural timber look heterogeneous vinyl flooring that combines durability and acoustic comfort.
                    p
                        strong
                            a(href="/") IVC Ultimo LVT Dry Back Plank :
                        |  Waterproof, easy to install, tough and simple to maintain luxury vinyl tiles.

                .case-detail-box
                    h4
                        img.icon(src="/icons/facts.svg", alt="image")
                        | Project Facts
                    p
                        strong Company&nbsp;
                        a(href="/") Fazyard Ltd
                    p
                        strong Flooring Contractor:&nbsp;
                        a(href="/") Gerry Woods

    section.project-gallery
        .container
            .header
                .header-box
                    +tag('PROJECT GALLERY', 'orange')
                .header-box
                    h2 Explore the Project

            .slider-handler
                .embla__dots
                .slider-controls
                    +prev
                    +next
            .slider-wrapper
                figure.slider-preview
                    img.image(src="/images/projects/gallery-1.png", alt="image")
                .embla.gallery-slider
                    .embla__container
                        each i in [2,1,2,1,2,1,2,1,2]
                            button.embla__slide
                                img.image(src=`/images/projects/gallery-${i}.png`, alt="image")

    section.testimonial
        .testimonial-header
            .header-box
                +tag('TESTIMONIALS', 'orange')
            .header-box
                h1
                    | Built on Trust,<br/>
                    span.blue Backed by Results.

        .embla.carousel-slider.centered
            .embla__container
                each i in [1,2]
                    .embla__slide.dark-slide
                        .slide-top
                            p.paragraph-xs
                                svg(width='70' height='14' viewBox='0 0 70 14' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg')
                                    path(d='m6.55 0 1.471 4.526h4.76L8.93 7.324l1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798L2.7 11.85l1.47-4.526L.32 4.526h4.76zM35 0l1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526L35 9.052l-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.759zM20.777 0l1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.76zm28.445 0 1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.76zm14.227 0 1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.76z' fill='currentColor')
                                | 4.7/5 Google Reviews
                            p.paragraph-xs October 13, 2024
                        .slide-header
                            h5 Niall Mc Donagh
                            h6
                                strong Niall McDonagh Roofing Services
                        .content-box
                            p “Laydex have been a trusted partner of ours for years. Their product range is excellent, and the technical support they provide makes a real difference on projects. Deliveries are always on time, communication is clear, and the team are a pleasure to deal with.
                            p We would happily recommend Laydex to anyone in the industry.”

                    .embla__slide.dark-slide
                        .slide-top
                            p.paragraph-xs
                                svg(width='70' height='14' viewBox='0 0 70 14' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg')
                                    path(d='m6.55 0 1.471 4.526h4.76L8.93 7.324l1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798L2.7 11.85l1.47-4.526L.32 4.526h4.76zM35 0l1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526L35 9.052l-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.759zM20.777 0l1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.76zm28.445 0 1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.76zm14.227 0 1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.76z' fill='currentColor')
                                | 4.7/5 Google Reviews
                            p.paragraph-xs October 13, 2024
                        .slide-header
                            h5 Brendan Walsh
                            h6
                                strong Director of Max roofing systems
                        .content-box
                            p “I have used RESITRIX now for four years on small and large contracts. It’s a fantasy material to work with. Easy to apply and most of all no time consuming metal on upstands or change of angle, no flame and fast installation. I would highly recommend it and beats other single Ply’s hands down.” Max Roofing

                    .embla__slide.dark-slide
                        .slide-top
                            p.paragraph-xs
                                svg(width='70' height='14' viewBox='0 0 70 14' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg')
                                    path(d='m6.55 0 1.471 4.526h4.76L8.93 7.324l1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798L2.7 11.85l1.47-4.526L.32 4.526h4.76zM35 0l1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526L35 9.052l-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.759zM20.777 0l1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.76zm28.445 0 1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.76zm14.227 0 1.47 4.526h4.76l-3.85 2.798 1.47 4.526-3.85-2.798-3.85 2.798 1.47-4.526-3.85-2.798h4.76z' fill='currentColor')
                                | 4.7/5 Google Reviews
                            p.paragraph-xs October 13, 2024
                        .slide-header
                            h5 PJ Costello
                            h6
                                strong Sterton Enterprises
                        .content-box
                            p “The results were class. I can’t believe it in all my years in roofing!”

